column5: Ive had more time than expected.  Ill show myself out?

Oh of course Brian! When hes awake that is! Sleeping like 20 hours a day hahahah.  And I couldnt stay away, OFC is like crack to me, im addicted ???  Thanks again everyone for the kind words and a few laughs!
Hahahahah, woulda been quick to call my good bud old ironmaker as well but I lost his phone number lol, which is probably good for both our cell phone bills???
